::Skulletron::

	Skulletron reached out and shook Feline's hand, grinning.

	"If either of you need me, I can be found outside, getting some fresh
air," Skulletron said, winking at Feline, and headed off towards the hatch.
 He opened the hatch, stepped outside and closed it.  He ran off a little
ways away and looked around.  He decided to contact Zardus, and let him
know how the mission was going.

	"Comm-link patch through to Zardus," Skulletron waited for a moment while
the com patched through to Zardus and prevented the transmission from being
recieved by other bots, "Zardus, this is Skulletron.  I am outside the
Cybertronian Fire.  Feline looks like she has some Maximal named Chordate
under her spell, and meanwhile, I have hopefully shortened the Predacons by
one bot, as I used my ability to establish a relationship between a Maximal
and a Predacon, and make the Predacon think she's a true Maximal.  I know
this might add to the Maximal forces but at least we stand a chance against
the tougher Predacons," Skulletron said and waited for a reply from Zardus.
